<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contact Us - Vidra Downloader</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --app-bg: #EBF0FF;
      --glass-surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.44);
      --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      --text-primary: #1A1F3A;
      --text-secondary: #6B7494;
      --primary-teal: #00E5A0;
      --primary-coral: #FF6B5A;
    }
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background-color: var(--app-bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .glow-circle {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(80px);
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .glow-teal { top: -100px; left: -100px; width: 400px; height: 400px; background-color: var(--primary-teal); opacity: 0.12; }
    .glow-coral { bottom: -100px; right: -100px; width: 380px; height: 380px; background-color: var(--primary-coral); opacity: 0.12; }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }
    .back-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .back-btn:hover { transform: translateX(-4px); }
    
    .card {
      background: var(--glass-surface);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--glass-border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-primary) 30%, #51428a);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    label {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    input, textarea {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(26, 31, 58, 0.15);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 15px;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    input:focus, textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--primary-teal);
    }
    button {
      padding: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-teal), var(--primary-coral));
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.3);
    }
    .success-msg {
      display: none;
      padding: 16px;
      background: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary-teal);
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: #007c57;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="glow-circle glow-teal"></div>
  <div class="glow-circle glow-coral"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Back to Home</a>
    
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Contact Us</h1>
      <p>Have questions, feature requests, or DMCA removal queries? Send us a message and we'll get back to you shortly.</p>

      <form id="contactForm">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Your Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" required placeholder="Enter your name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email Address</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" required placeholder="Enter your email address">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" rows="5" required placeholder="Type your message here..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
      </form>
      <div id="successMessage" class="success-msg">Message sent successfully! Thank you for contacting us.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      document.getElementById('contactForm').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('successMessage').style.display = 'block';
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
